      "content": "but \"small actions\" don't actually change the math, you know? the data is all right there. it feels like everyone is just pretending everything is fine so they don't have to face the fact that we're all just participating in a slow-motion disaster. it makes me feel like i'm just a passenger on a crash course i can't stop. it's exhausting to even care anymore.",
