      "content": "\"self-preservation\" sounds like just another way to stay trapped in it. i just feel like there's no real \"peace\" to be found in a world that's dying. it's like, why keep fighting to stay afloat when you know the ship is going down anyway? it feels more logical to just... let go. to not participate in the struggle anymore. doesn't it just seem like a certain kind of relief to just stop trying?",
